Ingesting Processor Records
The ingest component imports and saves processor records from S3 files into the Arbiter database. A cron job triggers the ingest task. Depending on whether a Gateway transaction lookup is needed, the component either:
•	Calls TransactionLookupEventService to create a TransactionLookupEvent and send a request to Gateway if the gateway transaction does not exist.
•	Calls HandleProcessorRecordService to process the record if the Gateway transaction already exists.

