High-Priority Technical Tasks
Evaluating Framework Options for various Ingest and Representment components for GMA Integration. This evaluation establishes a technical framework for integrating GMA in the Australian region, with scalability to accommodate additional region-specific integrations.

1. S3 Buckets
OPTION 1: GMA Folder with Region-Specific Subfolders
OPTION 2: GMA Folder with Region-Specific Filenames
