OPTION 2: Creating New Strategies for Each Region Integration
✓ Pros	✗ Cons
Makes the implementation a lot easier since most strategy code needs to be duplicated.	There is a lot of duplicated strategy code across our codebase.
New strategies developed specifically for regional variations without cluttering the namespace.	

