Using the existing Fiserv TransactionFinder
If we are using the current Fiserv chargeback models, we won't need to make changes to the TransactionFinder class. We can simply add a 'region' column to fiserv_transaction_details to keep track of records by region and improve the query performance.
The transaction details table is not only for bookkeeping — it has relevant columns used to find the gateway_transaction:
