OPTION 1: Single Transaction Finder Class + Single Transaction Details Table with Region Column
✓ Pros	✗ Cons
Easier to maintain one transaction_details table and transaction_finder class for all regions.	As data volume grows, the single table could become a performance bottleneck.
	If filter columns for transaction_details diverge for different regions, code complexity increases.

