Evaluating Arbiter and SnowGlobe Integration
We send financial events to Funding to signal them to disburse funds to merchants via Kafka on the topic arbiter_disputes. Funding sends us back the disbursement event via the Kafka topic funding_disputes_disbursement_global.
For GMA integration, we will continue publishing events to the same Kafka topic, to which SnowGlobe will also subscribe. SnowGlobe will now be responsible for calculating fees and the disbursement amount, and it will signal Funding to move the money (Funding will likely ignore Arbiter financial event messages). Similarly, SnowGlobe will be responsible for sending us the disbursement events.

